		<hr size="1">Guys, guys, we had a huge thread on this one.</P><P>With the FBSS, you're upping damage by 21%, along with a corresponding increase in taunt (from both damage and sheer attack speed).</P><P>When you're secondary tank, that extra 21% damage is worth far more than unneeded ac.  If you're main tank, I think the massively increased ability to retain aggro STILL beats your AC upgrade, and that's all the gauntlets are.</P><P>--------------------<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=481" target=_blank>Hizuka</a><BR>Swifttail Disciple<BR>Initiate of the Celestial Fists<BR>Innoruuk Server<BR><BR>"I do not feel obliged to believe that the same God who has endowed us with sense, reason, and intellect has intended us to forgo their use."<BR><i>- Galileo Galilei </i><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
